  <h2>Organizasyon Şeması</h2>
</blockquote>
<p></p>
<p><img class="img-fluid"
    src="https://sanalogrenme.bartin.edu.tr/draftfile.php/305/user/draft/848507780/Ba%C5%9Fl%C4%B1ks%C4%B1z%20Diyagram.drawio.png"
